::
++  orgs-pact
  ^-  item:smart
  =/  code  (cue orgs-contract)
  =/  id  (hash-pact:smart 0x1234.5678 0x1234.5678 default-town-id code)
  :*  %|  id
      0x1234.5678  ::  source
      0x1234.5678  ::  holder
      default-town-id
      [-.code +.code]
      ~
  ==
